room_title: Escape room "Zombie Roadhouse" by Breakout Escape Rooms in Lansing
review: Great way to spend time with the family and celebrate my birthday. We did the zombie room and got out with 7 minutes to spare. So much fun!

room_title: Escape room "Zombie Roadhouse" by Breakout Escape Rooms in Lansing
review: Challenging rooms, great fun and clever puzzles. We will definitely be back and bringing friends with us. My friend and I tried the Zombie Roadhouse and it was great.

room_title: Escape room "Zombie Roadhouse" by Breakout Escape Rooms in Lansing
review: Awesome time in a great (hard!) room. We tried, and failed, in the Zombie Roadhouse, but the experience couldn't have been better.Great host, fun time, and intense room.

room_title: Escape room "Zombie Roadhouse" by Breakout Escape Rooms in Lansing
review: Great time! Lots of fun. The wife and I were there for date night and it did not disappoint. The staff were very friendly and helpful. We did the "Zombie Roadhouse" and loved it. We recommend it and we'll be back soon.

room_title: Escape room "Zombie Roadhouse" by Breakout Escape Rooms in Lansing
review: Such a fun time. Definitely not easy. We did the Zombie room and did not make it out. Was told it's there hardest room. We have all decided that we will definitely come back to try out the other 2 rooms tho.
